'From Squeak4.1 of 17 April 2010 [latest update: #9957] on 25 April 2010 at 1:07:30 am'!"Change Set:		JapaneseInputAndClipboardFixForMacVM4-muDate:			1 July 2009Author:			Masashi UmezawaAdded a support of input and clipboard copy & paste in Japanese; a quick hack for Squeak 3.10 image on Mac VM 4.+."!ClipboardInterpreter subclass: #MacUTF8ClipboardInterpreter	instanceVariableNames: ''	classVariableNames: ''	poolDictionaries: ''	category: 'Multilingual-TextConversion'!!MacUTF8ClipboardInterpreter methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'mu 6/30/2009 23:45'!fromSystemClipboard: aString	^ aString convertFromWithConverter: UTF8TextConverter new! !!MacUTF8ClipboardInterpreter methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'mu 6/30/2009 23:45'!toSystemClipboard: text	| string |	"self halt."	string _ text asString.	string isAsciiString ifTrue: [^ string asOctetString].	string isOctetString ifTrue: [^ string "hmm"].	^ string convertToWithConverter: UTF8TextConverter new .! !